name: Sequin Men's Blazer
description:
Fits size Medium to Large. 
Multicolored Sequined mens blazer that buttons and unbuttons. All sequins were placed by hand at the pockets, neckline, left shoulder, and hem of sleeves. 2 silver applique angel wings at the back shoulder blades. A Perfect option for the stylish man who dares to Think Outside the Box! Enjoy :)

*Do not machine wash. Dry clean only

name: Hand Dyed Tribal Top (V Neck)
description:
MensWear size Medium
V Neck Asian/ African tribal top. 
Hand dyed (red, black and gray) silk cotton with faux beaver fur short sleeves. Red tribal pendant at neck line. Perfect for the hippie type of man who loves to try new prints. Enjoy :)


*Do no machine wash. Dry clean only

name: Peace of Mind (8x10) - Abstract
description:
Oil pastel art on 8 by 10 canvas. Abstract artwork by Octavia the artist
Real Emotions expressed with Color.

*Item will be sent in protective covering to preserve the oil coloring

name: Pink Flamingo Mini
description:
Size XS-Small (US Size 0-4)
This sleeveless reversible mini dress can be worn front ways or back ways due to the separating zipper and mirrored design technique. 
The silk/cotton fabric is printed with pink flamingos through out, up and down, and adorned with multicolored wooden beads at the base of the zipper and among the breast line; as well as one orange wooden button at the center of the reverse side. Perfect for a lunch date or walk on the beach. Enjoy!

*Machine wash lightly. Air dry for best results but it can be put in the dryer

name: Black Beaded Midrif Top
description:
One Size Fits Many (Small to Large - US sizes 0-11)
Hand beaded black belly shirt. 
The top itself is smooth black nylon/mesh fabric with the beaded crystals securely sewn for an intricate pattern. The black and silver Beads have been hand sewn in ovals, circles, lines, and flower like shapes. The back can be worn open or closed (use metal clasp at neck to close). It can be worn with or without an item under neath. Perfect for the club or for a sexy night at home! Enjoy :)

*Delicate. Do not machine wash
